SchemaItem.Name: GenerateTask_OnEventAgendaTaskChange
SchemaItem.M01:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?> <xsl:stylesheet xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" version="1.0" xmlns:AS="http://schema.advantages.cz/AsapFunctions" xmlns:date="http://exslt.org/dates-and-times" exclude-result-prefixes="AS date">
<xsl:template match="ROOT"> <ROOT> <xsl:apply-templates select="Event/EventAgenda/EventAgendaTask" /> </ROOT> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match="EventAgendaTask"> <xsl:variable name="ProjectTaskId" select="AS:GenerateId()" />
<xsl:choose> <!-- task exists, we update it !--> <xsl:when test="string(ProjectTask/@Id)"> <ProjectTask> <xsl:copy-of select="ProjectTask/@*[name()!='Name' and name()!='refProjectId' and name()!='refResourceId' and name()!='refResponsibleResourceId']" /> <xsl:attribute name="Name"><xsl:value-of select="@NewName" /></xsl:attribute> <xsl:attribute name="refProjectId"><xsl:value-of select="@refProjectId" /></xsl:attribute> <xsl:attribute name="refResourceId"><xsl:value-of select="@refNewResourceId" /></xsl:attribute> <xsl:attribute name="refResponsibleResourceId"><xsl:value-of select="@refNewResponsibleResourceId" /></xsl:attribute> <xsl:attribute name="MustFinishBefore"><xsl:value-of select="@NewMustFinishBefore" /></xsl:attribute>
<xsl:copy-of select="ProjectTask/*[name() != 'Description']"/>
<Description><xsl:value-of select="NewDescription"/></Description> </ProjectTask> </xsl:when> <!-- task does not exists, we create a new one !--> <xsl:otherwise> <EventAgendaTask> <xsl:copy-of select="@*"/> <xsl:attribute name="refProjectTaskId"><xsl:value-of select="$ProjectTaskId" /></xsl:attribute> <xsl:copy-of select="*[name() != 'ProjectTask']"/>
<ProjectTask Id="{$ProjectTaskId}" Name="{@NewName}" refProjectTaskDeliveryStateId="{AS:GetConstant('ProjectTaskDeliveryState_Planning')}" refProjectId="{@refProjectId}" IsSubroject="false" IsDelivery="false" refResourceId="{@refNewResourceId}" refResponsibleResourceId="{@refNewResponsibleResourceId}" MustFinishBefore="{@NewMustFinishBefore}" > <Description><xsl:value-of select="NewDescription"/></Description> </ProjectTask> </EventAgendaTask> </xsl:otherwise> </xsl:choose> </xsl:template> </xsl:stylesheet>

<xsl:template match="ROOT"> <ROOT> <xsl:apply-templates select="Event"/> </ROOT> </xsl:template>

SchemaItem.Name: GenerateMeeting_EventAgenda
SchemaItem.M01:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?> <xsl:stylesheet xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" version="1.0" xmlns:AS="http://schema.advantages.cz/AsapFunctions" xmlns:date="http://exslt.org/dates-and-times" exclude-result-prefixes="AS date">

<xsl:template match="ROOT"> <ROOT> <EventAgenda Id="{$EventAgenda_Id}" Name="Úkoly z minula" refProjectId="{Event/@refProjectId}" refEventId="{$Event_Id}" SortOrder="0"> <xsl:apply-templates select="Event/EventAgenda/EventAgendaTask" /> </EventAgenda> </ROOT> </xsl:template>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?> <xsl:stylesheet xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" version="1.0" xmlns:AS="http://schema.advantages.cz/AsapFunctions" xmlns:date="http://exslt.org/dates-and-times" exclude-result-prefixes="AS date">
<xsl:param name="dateStartPlanned"/>
<xsl:template match="ROOT"> <ROOT> <xsl:apply-templates select="EventTemplate"/> </ROOT> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match="EventTemplate"> <Event Id="{AS:GenerateId()}" Name="{@Name}" ReferenceCode="{AS:GetConstant('_auto_string')}" DateStartPlanned="{$dateStartPlanned}" DateEndPlanned="{AS:AddHours(AS:AddDays($dateStartPlanned, @EventDurationDays), @EventDurationHours)}" refEventStateId="{AS:GetConstant('EventState_Planned')}" refEventTypeId="{@refEventTypeId}" Location="{@Location}" refProjectId="{@refProjectId}" refRecordedByBusinessPartnerId="{@refRecordedByBusinessPartnerId}" >
<Description><xsl:value-of select="Description"/></Description> <LocationDirections><xsl:value-of select="LocationDirections"/></LocationDirections>
<xsl:apply-templates select="EventAgendaTemplate"/> <xsl:apply-templates select="EventRoleTemplate/BusinessPartnerRole[@Selected='true']"/> </Event> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match="EventAgendaTemplate"> <EventAgenda> <xsl:copy-of select="@*[name()!='Id' and name()!='refEvendTemplateId' and name()!='EndDate' and name()!='StartDate']" /> <xsl:attribute name="Id"><xsl:value-of select="AS:GenerateId()" /></xsl:attribute> <xsl:copy-of select="*" /> </EventAgenda> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match="BusinessPartnerRole"> <EventAttendee Id="{AS:GenerateId()}" refBusinessPartnerId="{@refBusinessPartnerId}" /> </xsl:template> </xsl:stylesheet>
